PN,36201
SC,0001
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F362A1782335894
OL,3,COldham to be one of the first towns
OL,4,Cinvestigated by the grooming gangs
OL,5,Cinquiry
OL,7,FOldham will be one of the first towns
OL,8,Fand cities to be investigated by the
OL,9,Fgrooming gangs inquiry.
OL,11,FThe inquiry is being chaired by
OL,12,FBaroness Anne Longfield and will
OL,13,Fcompel individuals and institutions to
OL,14,Fexplain their role in protecting
OL,15,Fchildren from being sexually abused.
OL,17,FThe scandal-hit probe is looking at
OL,18,Fhow grooming gangs operated in England
OL,19,Fand Wales and the actions of police,
OL,20,Fcouncils, health services, social care
OL,21,Fservices and schools.
OL,1,W~k4j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G1/9
OL,2,W/*%+.-' "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNW Eng NewsCThis Day FReg TV
FL,363,360,120,260,000,100
PN,36202
SC,0002
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F362A1782335894
OL,3,COldham to be one of the first towns
OL,4,Cinvestigated by the grooming gangs
OL,5,Cinquiry
OL,7,FThe announcement confirmed Oldham
OL,8,Falong with London, Bradford and
OL,9,FKeighley are the first areas to face
OL,10,Fso-called local investigations ` where
OL,11,Fserious failures have been identified
OL,12,Fin the response to child sexual
OL,13,Fexploitation by grooming gangs.
OL,15,FThe inquiry said it will look "in
OL,16,Fdetail at what happened in a specific
OL,17,Fplace ` including how children were
OL,18,Fidentified and protected, how
OL,19,Forganisations responded, how victims
OL,20,Fwere treated, and what needs to
OL,21,Fchange".
OL,26,@wD@_OU}D@GO]
OL,1,W~k4j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G2/9
OL,2,W/*%+.-' "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNW Eng NewsCThis Day FReg TV
FL,363,360,120,260,000,100
PN,36203
SC,0003
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F362A1782335894
OL,3,COldham to be one of the first towns
OL,4,Cinvestigated by the grooming gangs
OL,5,Cinquiry
OL,7,FThe decision reflects some of the
OL,8,F"most urgent" and "highest" priority
OL,9,Faspects of the inquiry's work but does
OL,10,Fnot mean that other places are "less
OL,11,Fimportant or that they will not be
OL,12,Fconsidered", it added.
OL,14,FDecisions on investigations in other
OL,15,Fareas of the country are expected to
OL,16,Fmade in the coming months.
OL,18,FThe Government has faced a stream of
OL,19,Fcriticism over its handling of the
OL,20,Fprobe.
OL,26,@pD@AOUpD@MO]pD@SOUpD@[O]rD@`OUtD@KO]
OL,1,W~k4j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G3/9
OL,2,W/*%+.-' "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNW Eng NewsCThis Day FReg TV
FL,363,360,120,260,000,100
PN,36204
SC,0004
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F362A1782335894
OL,3,COldham to be one of the first towns
OL,4,Cinvestigated by the grooming gangs
OL,5,Cinquiry
OL,7,FSir Keir Starmer initially resisted
OL,8,Fcalls for a national inquiry last year
OL,9,Fafter tech billionaire Elon Musk
OL,10,Fsparked a political row when he used
OL,11,Fhis X social media platform to attack
OL,12,Fthe Prime Minister over the long-
OL,13,Frunning scandal.
OL,15,FIn the wake of the U-turn on ordering
OL,16,Fthe inquiry, efforts to set up the
OL,17,Fbody and start work were fraught with
OL,18,Fdelays, resignations and rows about
OL,19,Fits scope.
OL,1,W~k4j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G4/9
OL,2,W/*%+.-' "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNW Eng NewsCThis Day FReg TV
FL,363,360,120,260,000,100
PN,36205
SC,0005
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F362A1782335894
OL,3,COldham to be one of the first towns
OL,4,Cinvestigated by the grooming gangs
OL,5,Cinquiry
OL,7,FDuring his election campaign, Labour
OL,8,Fleadership hopeful Andy Burnham
OL,9,Finsisted he "acted immediately" on
OL,10,Fgrooming gangs while he was mayor of
OL,11,FGreater Manchester and criticised
OL,12,Fothers for manipulating the facts.
OL,14,FFormer children's commissioner for
OL,15,FEngland Baroness Anne Longfield is
OL,16,Fleading the #65 million three-year
OL,17,Finquiry, which has the legal powers to
OL,18,Fcompel witnesses to give evidence and
OL,19,Frequire organisations to hand over
OL,20,Fdocuments.
OL,26,@qD@MOUqD@_O]
OL,1,W~k4j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G5/9
OL,2,W/*%+.-' "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNW Eng NewsCThis Day FReg TV
FL,363,360,120,260,000,100
PN,36206
SC,0006
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F362A1782335894
OL,3,COldham to be one of the first towns
OL,4,Cinvestigated by the grooming gangs
OL,5,Cinquiry
OL,7,FIt plans to hold its first public
OL,8,Fhearings by the end of the year.
OL,10,FSo far it has identified more than 800
OL,11,Frecommendations about tackling
OL,12,Fgrooming gangs, child sexual
OL,13,Fexploitation and abuse across numerous
OL,14,Freviews, reports and inquiries dating
OL,15,Fback to the 1990s with analysis
OL,16,Findicating there has been "significant
OL,17,Finconsistency in how these
OL,18,Frecommendations have been implemented".
OL,26,@xD@[OUzD@fO]
OL,1,W~k4j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G6/9
OL,2,W/*%+.-' "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNW Eng NewsCThis Day FReg TV
FL,363,360,120,260,000,100
PN,36207
SC,0007
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F362A1782335894
OL,3,COldham to be one of the first towns
OL,4,Cinvestigated by the grooming gangs
OL,5,Cinquiry
OL,7,FThe inquiry previously said it will
OL,8,Fexamine whether ethnicity, culture or
OL,9,Freligion influenced offending and if
OL,10,Fthey shaped the institutional response.
OL,12,FAny evidence of crimes uncovered will
OL,13,Fbe referred to Operation Beaconport,
OL,14,Fthe national police operation launched
OL,15,Flast year to review hundreds of
OL,16,Fpreviously closed investigations.
OL,1,W~k4j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G7/9
OL,2,W/*%+.-' "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNW Eng NewsCThis Day FReg TV
FL,363,360,120,260,000,100
PN,36208
SC,0008
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F362A1782335894
OL,3,COldham to be one of the first towns
OL,4,Cinvestigated by the grooming gangs
OL,5,Cinquiry
OL,7,FBaroness Longfield said: "The
OL,8,Finquiry's task is to find out why this
OL,9,Fcatastrophic failure of the state
OL,10,Fhappened and continues to happen, to
OL,11,Festablish why victims and survivors of
OL,12,Fabuse were failed, and to hold to
OL,13,Faccount those institutions and
OL,14,Findividuals who failed them."
OL,26,@oD@ZOUvD@]O]
OL,1,W~k4j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G8/9
OL,2,W/*%+.-' "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNW Eng NewsCThis Day FReg TV
FL,363,360,120,260,000,100
PN,36209
SC,0009
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F362A1782335894
OL,3,COldham to be one of the first towns
OL,4,Cinvestigated by the grooming gangs
OL,5,Cinquiry
OL,7,FShe said the hearings will "help us to
OL,8,Festablish what national institutions
OL,9,Fand services should have been doing to
OL,10,Fimplement these findings and to
OL,11,Fprotect children from abuse and harm `
OL,12,Fand what, if any, progress has been
OL,13,Fmade in areas where investigations
OL,14,Fhave taken place", adding: "We are
OL,15,Fdetermined that our work ensures that
OL,16,Fno further inquiries into grooming
OL,17,Fgangs will ever be needed."
OL,26,@oD@\OUvD@QO]vD@\OUyD@[O]
OL,1,W~k4j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G9/9
